---

Stellar Guru Contracts

Stealth address smart contracts for the Stellar Guru multichain privacy platform. EVM contracts are implemented in Solidity (Hardhat) and Stellar contracts are implemented in Soroban/Rust.

The contract suite provides the core on-chain infrastructure for privacy-preserving payments using stealth addresses. Every payment generates a fresh one-time stealth address so on-chain observers cannot link the sender, recipient, or transaction history.


